  "content": "<p>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.XOJpjqmBzwE4R4n0]{(Index) Environment}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.mmx5KJLX4vsGZ7vz]{3.1. Traps}</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.3f7JZIvocYHSXzvd]{3.1.1. Elements of a Trap}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.XIjPXv3Qe62dFI3Z]{3.1.2. List of Traps}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.IYnf1w2TjcHO2ExM]{3.1.3. Designing a Trap}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.gGGKd0tOkXUqLZya]{3.1.4. Wilderness Traps}</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 423</em></p>\n<p>Designing new traps is a simple process. Start by deciding what type of trap you want to create.</p>\n<h2>Mechanical Traps</h2>\n<p>Simply select the elements you want the trap to have and add up the adjustments to the trap&rsquo;s Challenge Rating that those elements require (see Table 13&ndash;3) to arrive at the trap&rsquo;s final CR. From the CR you can derive the DC of the Craft (traps) checks a character must make to construct the trap (see @JournalEntry[4dz26JMCoC0DjKkr]{3.1.3.5. Craft DCs for Mechanical Traps}).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Table 13-3: CR Modifiers for Mechanical Traps</h2>\n<table style=\"height: 560px; width: 61.9914%;\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\" scope=\"col\">Feature</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\" scope=\"col\">CR Modifier</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Perception DC</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">15 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">-1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">16-20</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">21-25</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">26-29</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">30 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Disable Device DC</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">15 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">-1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">16-20</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">21-25</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">26-29</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">30 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Reflex Save DC (Pit or Other Save-Dependent Trap</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">15 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">-1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">16-20</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">21-25</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">26-29</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">30 or higher</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Attack Bonus (Melee or Ranged Attack Trap)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">+0 or lower</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">-2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">+1 to +5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">-1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">+6 to +10</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">+11 to +15</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">+16 to +20</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Touch attack</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Damage/Effect</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Average damage</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1 per 10 points of average damage</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Miscellaneous Features</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Alchemical device</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">Level of spell mimicked</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Automatic reset</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Liquid</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Multiple targets (non-damage)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Never miss</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 62.9834%; height: 16px;\">Proximity or visual trigger</td>\n<td style=\"width: 36.7551%; height: 16px;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width: 41.066%;\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\" scope=\"col\">Poison</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\">CR of poison</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Black adder venom</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Black lotus extract</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Bloodroot</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Blue whinnis</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Burnt othur fumes</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Deathblade</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Dragon bile</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Giant wasp poison</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Greenblood oil</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Insanity mist</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Large scorpion venom</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Malyass root paste</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Medium spider venom</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Nitharit</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Purple worm poison</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Sassone leaf residue</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Shadow essence</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Small centipede poison</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Terinav root</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Ungol dust</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 65.8089%;\">Wyvern poison</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5375%; text-align: center;\">+5</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Magic Traps</h2>\n<p>As with mechanical traps, decide what elements you want and then determine the CR of the resulting trap (see Table 13&ndash;4). If a player character wants to design and construct a magic trap, he, or an ally, must have the Craft Wondrous Item feat. In addition, he must be able to cast the spell or spells that the trap requires&mdash;or he must be able to hire an NPC to cast the spells for him.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Table 13-4: CR Modifiers for Magic Traps</h2>\n<table style=\"width: 55.3214%;\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 47.793%;\" scope=\"col\">Feature</td>\n<td style=\"width: 51.5534%;\" scope=\"col\">CR Modifier</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 47.793%;\">Highest-level spell effect</td>\n<td style=\"width: 51.5534%;\">+Spell level</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 47.793%;\">Damaging spell effect</td>\n<td style=\"width: 51.5534%;\">+1 per 10 points of average damage</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
}
